PDF conversion will help make it easier to view and print form. 
We want a form to open as a PDF and have all of its pages, so it can be printed all at once
First you can get the View(HTML/CSS) to get converted. 
You can also have the PDF save to a specific path on the computer.

Here are some sources that help explain this process using the gem PDFKit

----------            https://github.com/pdfkit/PDFKit

----------            http://railscasts.com/episodes/220-pdfkit

